org.telesocial.rest.api
Interface ConferenceTemplate

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConferenceTemplateImpl
public interface ConferenceTemplate

Allows several operations on existing conference calls. Conferences can be created with TelesocialClient.createConference(boolean, org.telesocial.rest.api.resources.HasNetworkId...). Instances of ConferenceTemplate can be created with TelesocialClient.conference(HasConferenceId)

Author:
Shamaila Tahir
See Also:
TelesocialClient.createConference(boolean, HasNetworkId...), TelesocialClient.conference(HasConferenceId)
